Our philosophy is banks should be managed primarily to <b>create value</b> for shareholders.  We believe a proven path to success is to carefully <b>understand, plan and manage</b> the creation of this value by targeting a small number of forward-looking performance metrics.  And this requires detailed understanding, planning and managing of those metrics <b>relative to peers</b>.<br><br>
		
